org.batfish.datamodel.acl.explanation

Class AclLineMatchExprSetBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.datamodel.acl.explanation.AclLineMatchExprSetBuilder
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConjunctsBuilder, DisjunctsBuilder

    public abstract class AclLineMatchExprSetBuilder
extends Object
    Represents a set of AclLineMatchExprs -- either a set of conjuncts or a set of disjuncts. Uses BDDs to detect and remove redundant members.
